description: Overnight Oats is the most fun and convenient breakfast for busy mornings, and the recipe options are endless! Just ask Alexa to open Quaker and follow along as she walks you through our top Overnight Oats recipes, leaving you with a delicious and refreshing breakfast you can enjoy tomorrow ? no further prep required! For even more recipes and info, visit QuakerOvernightOats.com
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Quaker for a recipe
Alexa, ask Quaker what's for breakfast
name: Quaker
shortDescription:
Create delicious, no-fuss Overnight Oats recipes for on-the-go mornings with Quaker.

To use the Quaker Alexa skill, try saying?

"Alexa, open Quaker"
